Product Name: SHCA - Self-Hosted Chat Application
Developed by Makrs Studio
----------
SHCA is a self-hosted chat web application. It is a private, secure, and encrypted chat application. It uses Nodejs and npm to build and install. This makes it very easy to use and install. You can also use it on your own server if you want.

SHCA provides a dedicated web interface that lets you easily manage your users, add new users, and see statistics about your chats. Our modern design makes it easy to use. Our security features make it very hard for anyone to hack or access your account.

SHCA offers a variety of features that make chatting easy and fun. We have a chat widget that lets you easily add chat room members without having to leave the web interface. We also have some other features that make it easy to chat with others around the world.

SHCA is a great tool for anyone who wants a chat application that is easy to use, secure, and encrypted. It will help you keep in touch with friends and family across the globe.


SHCA is the best way to make your website your own. It's a self-hosted chat web application that allows you to add an HTML component to make your website your own. With SHCA, you can:

-Have your own chat windows that are fully customizable

-Add shortcodes to control everything from color of chats to background images

-Use any font and colour scheme you like

-Attach any photos or videos to your chats

-Setup multiple user levels so that everyone has their own chat room and can see who's online at the same time

-Control everything from who enters chats to when and how long chats are held

-Built in instant messaging features so you don't have to worry about installing any clients

With SHCA, you can host your own chat server or have others use your server for free. Plus, with our advanced server settings, you can even set it up so that your server doesn't have to be online at all!

SHCA is a self-hosted chat web application designed with Boostrap. It allows you to easily and privately send messages to anyone around the world. Whether you're at home or on the go, SHCA will make your life easier.

SHCA is quick, easy to use, and safe. It only requires a single email account to register and use. Plus, you can use SHCA on any device, even your phone. So why wait? Download SHCA today and start communicating with ease.
